snippet.title: John Lennon Exposed the Illuminati in Rare Interview?

localized.description:
Did John Lennon warn about the Illuminati?  The former Beatles band member spoke out about the dangers of war and poverty, but many believe that in one particular interview he may have warned the world about the Illuminati agenda, leading many to believe this led to his assassination.  What is the truth?  Watch and learn.

   BIO: 
Mark Dice is a media analyst and bestselling author who specializes in exposing the power mainstream media and celebrities have on shaping our culture.  He has been featured on the History Channel's Decoded, Ancient Aliens, and America's Book of Secrets; Conspiracy Theory with Jesse Ventura, Secret Societies of Hollywood on E! Channel, America Declassified on the Travel Channel, and is a frequent guest on Coast to Coast AM, The Alex Jones Show, and more.  His viral videos have received more than 140 million views and have received international media attention.
